<div class="navbar">
  <div class="navbar-logo">
    <%= image_tag "golf-logo.png", class: "logo-image"%>
  </div>
  <div class="navbar-links">
    <a><%=link_to 'Home', home_path%></a>
    <% if user_signed_in? %>
      <a><%= link_to "Dashboard", user_dashboard_path %></a>
      <a><%=link_to "Log Out", destroy_user_session_path%></a>
    <% else %>
      <a><%=link_to "Demo", new_user_session_path %></a>
      <a><%=link_to 'About', about_path%></a>
    <% end %>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="title-container">
  <h1>GolfConnect</h1>
  <h3>Connect better with your members and their guests.</h3>
</div>
<div class="flex-container-2">
  <div class="idea-container">
    <h2>The Idea</h2>
    <h4>Connecting with other golfers at your club is hard. Now with GolfConnect you can make tee times, share photos, stories and update your friends on which hole you just aced! All of this is confined within the club. A private platform to talk with other members</h4>
  </div>
  <div class="image-container">
    <%= image_tag "how-it-works.png", class: "how-it-works-image"%>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="flex-container">
  <div class="image-container">
    <%= image_tag "idea-pic.png", class: "idea-pic-image"%>
  </div>
  <div class="idea-container">
    <h2>How it works</h2>
    <h4>You must be invited to join the clubs ConnectAccount. As the club administrator you can post about upcoming tournaments, tee times for the next weeks or give your members new deals in the ProShop </h4>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="flex-container-2">
  <div class="idea-container">
    <h2>Getting Started</h2>
    <h4>Try it out today! You can preview the application and see what GolfConnect could do for your club and its members</h4>
    <%= link_to new_user_session_path do %>
      <div type="button" class="btn btn-outline-dark btn-lg">Try Out</div>
    <% end %>
  </div>
  <div class="image-container">
    <%= image_tag "try-out.png", class: "how-it-works-image"%>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="flex-container">
  <div class="image-container">
    <%= image_tag "project.png", class: "idea-pic-image"%>
  </div>
  <div class="idea-container">
    <h2>The Project</h2>
    <h4>This project is on going. It focuses is Ruby on Rails as a backend application while using a React frontend framework. More information is found on my Github. </h4>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="footer">
  <div class="footer-links">
    <a href="https://github.com/m-cwalina/ConnectGolf"><i class="fab fa-github"></i></a>
    <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/matthew-cwalina/"><i class="fab fa-linkedin"></i></a>
  </div>
  <div class="footer-copyright">
    <p>Created by Matthew Cwalina</p>
  </div>
</div>
